WEBVTT

00:02.048 --> 00:04.083
NATHAN: This is why we came here.

00:04.083 --> 00:06.051
Oh, nothing else matters.

00:06.052 --> 00:10.007
Gabriel. They've seen him, standing
by the lake, right where he drowned.

00:10.008 --> 00:11.999
William Payne,
from Marshfield Estate.

00:12.000 --> 00:15.059
When I was looking for Charlie,
I saw lights rushing towards me.

00:15.060 --> 00:16.087
There's a woman.

00:16.088 --> 00:19.035
A ghost. She has been present
from the very beginning,

00:19.036 --> 00:21.008
throughout all these hauntings.

00:22.044 --> 00:24.059
GIDEON: I thought Mr Denning
was going to end this.

00:24.060 --> 00:26.083
You're not welcome here, Denning!

00:26.084 --> 00:29.059
None of them will work for us again.
You do realise that?

00:29.060 --> 00:31.059
Why should there be
a scientific explanation?

00:31.060 --> 00:32.095
If there isn't, I'm going mad.

00:32.095 --> 00:34.015
That's Gabriel.

00:34.016 --> 00:36.063
I was going to tell you.
When, exactly?

00:36.064 --> 00:37.084
Leave us alone!
No! No!

00:40.040 --> 00:43.012
I can't abandon my husband, not now.

